
<div class="ncce-aside landing-page__aside">
  <% unless @programme.user_completed_diagnostic?(current_user) %>
    <p class='govuk-body-s'>Start your teaching journey by taking the diagnostic quiz to see how confident you feel about the various parts of the GCSE curriculum.</p>
  <% end %>
  <% if @online_achievements.size.positive? || @face_to_face_achievements.size.positive? %>
    <% if @programme.enough_activites_for_test?(current_user) %>
      <% if @user_programme_assessment.failed_last_attempt? %>
        <p class='govuk-body-s'>Bad luck! The test is available for another try.</p>
      <% else %>
        <p class='govuk-body-s'>Your test is ready. Feeling confident? Good luck!</p>
      <% end %>
      <p class='govuk-body-s'>If youâ€™re not yet feeling confident about teaching GCSE computer science you can do more stuff</p>
    <% else %>
    <p class='govuk-body-s'>Continue your journey towards feeling confident about teaching GCSE computer science. You can do as much training as you like as part of this programme.</p>
    <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <p class='govuk-body-s'>Taken the diagnostic but not yet chosen a course.</p>
  <% end %>
  <p class='govuk-body-s'>Book or join a course today</p>
  <%= link_to 'Find a course', courses_path(certificate: @programme.slug), class: 'govuk-button button' %>
  <p class='govuk-body-s'>We are happy to support you along the way. Call 020 0234 5678 or email <%= mail_to 'info@teachcomputing.org', 'info@teachcomputing.org' %> if you need to speak to someone.</p>
</div>
